00:14:08.436 --> 00:14:12.016
erroneous signals that are really a reflection of the technical noise.

238
00:14:13.156 --> 00:14:16.856
And so to ground your insights with data in

239
00:14:16.976 --> 00:14:20.236
context, there's a paper that I published in "Cancer Research" in

