00:47:52.256 --> 00:47:56.156
just at the gene level, but at the variant level in the cancer type context

811
00:47:56.596 --> 00:48:00.146
for the clinical significance of individual variants that we detect in our

812
00:48:00.216 --> 00:48:04.196
MSK-IMPACT tests. And there's a very specific protocol

813
00:48:04.236 --> 00:48:07.516
that's followed and specific tiering criteria from

814
00:48:08.296 --> 00:48:11.246
FDA-approved treatments to investigational

815
00:48:12.076 --> 00:48:13.596
therapies in preclinical data.

816
00:48:15.616 --> 00:48:19.256
And even within this framework, there's important opportunities for AI, given the

