00:48:31.056 --> 00:48:35.036
how we interact with these databases and

821
00:48:35.056 --> 00:48:38.796
knowledge bases, and even the computer systems that we

822
00:48:38.856 --> 00:48:42.636
use. So AI, large language

823
00:48:42.696 --> 00:48:45.736
models are an obvious application for this type of

824
00:48:46.296 --> 00:48:49.716
clinical decision support and interpretation of variants.

